Name: BARE BOOB BRAWLERZ: POWER CLAW
About the game: Back after 1.7 yizzears with another JUG-o'naut title! BBB: Power Claw! See the game play video to get a feel for this game! Fight through 20 levels of 'side scrolling boobling brawler brutality' and engage in several 1 on 1 boss battles as you take control of four different topless brawlers in this ... uh ... brawler. This is a one player game that celebrates the only physics that matter at the end of the day. Bare Boob Brawlerz plays with a retro feel and is meant to be enjoyed humorously and CASUALLY. Don't buy it if you are expecting a $60 triple A fighting game. I mean seriously. Also from X-MiGuPLAY: 'X-MiGu Fighters ... the sequel to Stripper Anya!' / / /
